overview: Pre-Show for the 2022 WWE Premium Live Event Clash at the Castle, live from the Principality Stadium in Cardiff Wales on September 3rd 2022. Featuring the six-man tag match Madcap Moss and The Street Profits (Angelo Dawkins and Montez Ford) against Austin Theory and Alpha Academy (Chad Gable and Otis)
